(274, 2, 34, NULL, 6, '<p>Les trois premiers termes d\'une suite ${bs}displaystyle (I_n)_{n{bs}geq 0}$ sont représentés ci-dessous.</p><p><img data-cke-saved-src=\"https://my-adele.fr/question_pictures/2/349a579a.png\" src=\"https://my-adele.fr/question_pictures/2/349a579a.png\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 120px;\"><img data-cke-saved-src=\"https://my-adele.fr/question_pictures/2/3568378b.png\" src=\"https://my-adele.fr/question_pictures/2/3568378b.png\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 120px;\"><img data-cke-saved-src=\"https://my-adele.fr/question_pictures/2/36bd8f02.png\" src=\"https://my-adele.fr/question_pictures/2/36bd8f02.png\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 120px;\"><br></p><p>Dans ce cas, la réponse la plus probable est:</p><p style=\"line-height: 25px;\"><img src=\"/bundles/common/images/distracteur2.png\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;\">$$I_n={bs}int_0^n {bs}dfrac{x}{1+x+x^2}{bs}mathrm{d}x$$</p><p style=\"line-height: 25px;\"><img src=\"/bundles/common/images/bonne_reponse2.png\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;\">$$I_n={bs}int_0^1 {bs}dfrac{x^n}{1+x+x^2}{bs}mathrm{d}x$$</p><p style=\"line-height: 25px;\"><img src=\"/bundles/common/images/distracteur2.png\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;\">$$ I_n={bs}int_0^1 {bs}dfrac{x}{1+x+x^n}{bs}mathrm{d}x$$</p>', '{\"id\":274,\"enonce\":\"<p>Les trois premiers termes d\'une suite $ (I_n)_{n\\\\geq 0}$ sont représentés ci-dessous.</p><p><img src=\\\"/question_pictures/2/349a579a.png\\\" class=\\\"u-max-full-width\\\"><img src=\\\"/question_pictures/2/3568378b.png\\\" class=\\\"u-max-full-width\\\"><img src=\\\"/question_pictures/2/36bd8f02.png\\\" class=\\\"u-max-full-width\\\"></p><p>Dans ce cas, la réponse la plus probable est:</p>\",\"explication\":\"\",\"bonneReponse\":2,\"reponses\":[\"$$I_n=\\\\int_0^n \\\\dfrac{x}{1+x+x^2}\\\\mathrm{d}x$$\",\"$$I_n=\\\\int_0^1 \\\\dfrac{x^n}{1+x+x^2}\\\\mathrm{d}x$$\",\"$$ I_n=\\\\int_0^1 \\\\dfrac{x}{1+x+x^n}\\\\mathrm{d}x$$\"],\"feedbacks\":[\"\",\"\",\"\"],\"aide\":\"\"}', '